<bug>
    <id>44133</id>
    <title>Background colour in Libreoffice Draw does not change</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">When going into Tools --&gt; Options --&gt; Appearance --&gt; Application Background and changing the colour to something other than the default in Libreoffice Draw, nothing happens.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">When doing the same thing in Writer or Impress, the application background changes colour (the desired behaviour).</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">I also have noticed this problem in the Libreoffice 3.4 series.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
